    <p class="pTitle">Delivery</p>

    <p>We offer $10 flat rate delivery fee on ALL of our products and 90% of
       our orders will be dispatched the next working day.  Once your item has been dispatched
       you will receive an email with your unique tracking code.</p>

    <p>We use TNT Express Australia and aim to get you purchase to you within 7 days. However we 
       have warehouses all over the world and if your product isn’t in Australia it will take between 
       7 to 14 days.</p>  

    <p>We also offer a pick up option on certain items. If you are located in Queensland and would like 
       to pick your item up from our warehouse 2/315 Archerfield Rd, Richlands QLD 4077 email us after 
       placing your order on info@online2shop.com.au and we will tell you if your item is available 
       to pickup.</p>  


       <p class="pTitle">Returns Policy</p>
        <p>
            Hopefully everything has arrived safe and sound. 
            I hope that you find your new purchase to be as amazing as you thought it would be.
            However should you be unhappy with your order for any reasons please follow our return instructions. 
        </p>

        <p class="pTitle">Return instructions</p>

        <p>Broken or damaged items only:  Please send a photo of the damage to our email address <a href="mailto:info@online2shop.com.au">info@online2shop.com.au</a>.  
           Once we receive the photo we will arrange a replacement and either advise you to dispose of the item or return it to us.  
           Please do not return anything unless you have been advised to do so.

           </p>
        <p> Returns for any other reason within 60 days of purchase:  
            If you would like to return your item for any other reason email us on <a href="mailto:info@online2shop.com.au">info@online2shop.com.au</a> so we can be 
            expecting the item.  Please repackage the item and send it to our postal address 2/315 Archerfield Rd, 
            Richlands QLD 4077.</p>





